Transactional Bulk SMS Coimbatore :
Transactional SMS Coimbatore is mainly used for direct interaction between business & consumer. It is used in corporate field. TRAI introduce this category to limit the unsolicited communication. The content of SMS decides its category. Usually transactional SMS are such messages that contain informative content: like banks update to registered customers, about transaction, updating about live events like voting etc.
